            <td><p class="para">Ice hockey is a fast team sport that is played on ice skating, and with dedicated sticks with a curved blade, which is used to strike a vulcanized rubber disc into the opponent's goal to score it. The team that scored more goals than its opponent is the winner of the game.</p></td>
